snippet.title: GODDESS OF VICTORY: NIKKE | Protocol Squad Promo Video
snippet.description:
Check out the official release of the PV for 【Squad: Protocol】! 

A squad under the Central Strategic Intelligence Agency. They mainly handle the spread of intelligence reports within the Ark and gather the intelligence needed by the central government.

※ This video is a scene under development and there may be some changes at the time of launch.
